      "text": [
        " «يُومِئُ إِيمَاءً."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1338 - Sama'a ibn Mehran asked Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) about a man who is captured by polytheists, and the time for prayer arrives, but he fears that they will prevent him from praying.\nImam (as) said: \"He should pray by gesturing.\""
        ]
      }
